These are Puzzles for 2x7 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-1::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  electrician, entrepreneur, mechanic, paramedic, photographer, social-worker, videographer
There 7 different types of food: cucumber, radish, peas, grapes, asparagus, lettuce, cranberry
 1. the paramedic is on the left of the person eating grapes##1
 2. the person eating asparagus is the paramedic##1
 3. the videographer is on the right of the social-worker##1
 4. the person eating peas is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 5. the mechanic is in the middle##1
 6. the person eating cucumber is on the far left##1
 7. the photographer is the person eating cucumber##1
 8. the electrician is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 9. the person eating peas is on the left of the person eating radish##1
10. the person eating grapes is on the left of the mechanic##1
11. the videographer is on the right of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |      3       |    4     |      5      |       6       |      7       |
| Job           | photographer | paramedic | entrepreneur | mechanic | electrician | social-worker | videographer |
| Food   | cucumber    | asparagus   | grapes      | lettuce | peas    | radish    | cranberry         |

