.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-2::.
7 different pets are kept: turtle, rabbit, dog, bird, chinchilla, goldfish, hedgehog
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: d&b, funk, gospel, pop, punk, rock, soul
 1. the fan of punk is the owner of the bird##1
 2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the fan of soul##1
 3. the fan of rock is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the fan of funk##1
 5. the owner of the bird is on the right of the fan of pop##1
 6. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 7. the fan of punk is in the middle##1
 8. the fan of punk is on the right of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 9. the fan of soul is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
10. the owner of the bird is on the left of the fan of d&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |     4     |     5     |     6      |    7     |
| Pet          | turtle | rabbit | chinchilla | bird | goldfish | hedgehog | dog |
| Music-Genre   | funk      | gospel   | pop   | punk      | d&b       | soul       | rock     |

