.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-4::.
The people use 7 different means of transport: scooter, tram, taxi, skateboard, bike, motorbike, subway
There are 7 different nationalities: argentine, australian, egyptian, indian, indonesian, nigerian, thai
 1. the person driving the bike is the australian##1
 2. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 3. the nigerian is on the right of the egyptian##1
 4. the argentine is on the right of the person driving the bike##1
 5. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 6. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1
 7. the egyptian is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 8. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the nigerian##1
 9. the person driving the taxi is the indonesian##1
10. the indonesian is on the left of the person driving the tram##1
11. the thai is the person driving the tram##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |     4      |  5   |     6      |     7     |
| Transport   | motorbike    | subway     | skateboard     | taxi      | tram | bike      | scooter     |
| Nationality   | indian | egyptian | nigerian | indonesian | thai | australian | argentine |

