.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-5::.
The people have 7 different hobbies: board-games, cooking, drawing, gardening, magic-tricks, sudoku, video-games
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: family, horror, martial-arts, crime, adventure, thriller, mystery
 1. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person watching mystery movies##1
 2. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the person watching thriller movies is in the middle##1
 4. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 5. the person watching adventure movies is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
 7. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 8. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
 9. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
10. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |      5      |      6       |      7      |
| Hobby   | cooking | drawing | sudoku     | gardening | video-games | magic-tricks | board-games |
| Movie-Genre     | mystery   | martial-arts    | adventure | thriller     | family         | crime     | horror        |

