.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-7::.
The people prefer 7 different music-genres: blues, metal, punk, house, folk, electronic, trance
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, jet-ski, motorbike, roller, skateboard, snowmobile, trike
 1. the fan of electronic is on the left of the person driving the jet-ski##1
 2. the fan of house is on the left of the fan of folk##1
 3. the fan of trance is the person driving the roller##1
 4. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the fan of metal##1
 5. the fan of electronic is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
 7. the person driving the boat is the fan of punk##1
 8. the fan of folk is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the trike is on the right of the fan of trance##1
10. the person driving the boat is on the right of the fan of metal##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3   |      4       |     5      |     6     |   7   |
| Music-Genre   | blues  | trance | house | folk | electronic     | metal | punk |
| Transport     | snowmobile | roller      | trike | motorbike    | skateboard | jet-ski   | boat  |

