.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-8::.
7 different games are played: billiard, backgammon, go, whist, monopoly, domino, snooker
The people use 7 different means of transport: boat, helicopter, quad-bike, roller, scooter, taxi, train
 1. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 2. the person driving the train is in the middle##1
 3. the person playing backgammon is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
 5. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the roller##1
 6. the person playing go is the person driving the roller##1
 7. the person playing domino is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person playing whist##1
 9. the person playing domino is in the middle##1
10. the person playing go is on the right of the person playing billiard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |       4       |     5      |     6      |    7    |
| Game       | backgammon   | whist | snooker | domino | billiard     | go | monopoly |
| Transport   | quad-bike | taxi      | boat        | train         | helicopter | roller     | scooter |

