.:: Puzzle 2x7-Level-1-9::.
There 7 different types of food: broccoli, corn, grapes, kiwi, papaya, radish, watermelon
The people grow 7 different varities of flowers: rose, azalea, daisy, aconite, dahlia, balloon-flower, zinnia
 1. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person eating watermelon##1
 2. the person who growsaconite is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
 3. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person eating papaya##1
 4. the person who growsrose is in the middle##1
 5. the person who growsaconite is the person eating broccoli##1
 6. the person who growsdahlia is the person eating radish##1
 7. the person eating kiwi is on the right of the person eating grapes##1
 8. the person who growsrose is on the left of the person who growsdahlia##1
 9. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the person eating corn##1
10. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person who growsazalea##1
11. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person eating radish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2     |   3    |    4     |   5    |     6      |   7    |
