 5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 6. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
 7. the person who's sport is water-polo is on the left of the person who's sport is swimming##1
 8. the person watching musical movies is the person who's sport is climbing##1
 9. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
10. the person who's sport is volleyball is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |   4    |    5    |     6     |    7     |
