 4. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
 5. the person driving the subway is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
 6. the person driving the roller is the person traveling to paris##1
 7. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person traveling to venice##1
 8. the person traveling to prague is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 9. the person traveling to london is in the middle##1
10. the person driving the subway is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |     3     |      4       |  5   |     6     |     7      |
| City   | hannover | paris | venice   | london | nizza | prague | boston        |
| Transport     | snowmobile | roller | quad-bike | bike         | bus  | subway    | skateboard |

